title: Fantasy Busts & Values for 2022 + PP...R Leagues - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/25
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, bust & value picks for 2022! Find out who Andy, Mike, and Jason are especially avoiding and targeting in fantasy football drafts! Plus, a new edition of Best Ball Breakdown focusing on the impact of rookie WRs. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 25th, 2022.

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
